history.proof: intros x y H. qsimpl use: dist_aux.

exceptions.tactic: apply dist_aux in H as [H1 H2].
exceptions.exn: Unable to find an instance for the variables x, y.

original: intros x y H. apply dist_aux in H as [H1 H2]. split. - apply left_prefix in H1. auto. - apply right_prefix in H1. auto.
